params.RcvrType: An identifier for the type of receiver (1 for wholesaler, 2 for distributor).
params._description: A brief description of the batch.
params._manufacturerAddr: The address of the manufacturer creating the batch.
params._quantity: The quantity of commodity in the batch.
params._rawAddr: An array of addresses representing the raw materials used in the batch.
params._receiverAddr: The address of the receiver of the batch.
params._transporterAddr: An array of addresses representing the transporters involved in the shipment.

returns._0: A uint representing the current status of the commodity batch.

returns._description: A brief description of the commodity batch.
returns._quantity: The quantity of commodity in the batch.
returns._rawAddr: An array of addresses representing the raw materials used in the batch.
returns._transporterAddr: An array of addresses representing the transporters involved in the shipment.

returns.WDP: An array of 3 addresses representing the wholesaler, distributor, and customer.

params._transporterAddr: The address of the transporter picking up the commodity.

params._receiverAddr: The address of the receiver (either wholesaler or distributor).

returns._0: A uint representing the new status of the commodity batch.

params._transporterAddr: The address of the transporter to add.

getBatchIDStatus().notice: Returns the current status of the commodity batch.

getCommodityInfo().notice: Returns information about the commodity batch.

getWDC().notice: Returns the addresses of the wholesaler, distributor, and customer.

pickCommodity(address).notice: Updates the status of the commodity batch when it is picked up by a transporter.

receivedCommodity(address).notice: Updates the status of the commodity batch when it is received by a wholesaler or distributor.

receivedDtoC(address).notice: Updates the status of the commodity batch when it is received by the customer from the distributor.

receivedWtoD(address).notice: Updates the status of the commodity batch when it is received by the distributor from the wholesaler.

sendDtoC(address,address).notice: Updates the customer address and status of the commodity batch when it is sent from the distributor to the customer.

sendWtoD(address,address).notice: Updates the distributor address and status of the commodity batch when it is sent from the wholesaler to the distributor.

updateTransporterArray(address).notice: Adds a transporter to the array of transporters involved in the shipment.
